          "date": "2026-03-08 01:48:46.000000000",
          "tz": 420
        },
        "subject": "LU-17916 osc: switch to struct folio",
        "message": "LU-17916 osc: switch to struct folio\n\nSwitch from struct page and page based API to struct folio\nand the folio API.\n\nWhen getting user pages with get_user_pages et. al. as\nis used for direct i/o mechanical conversion of page to\nfolio has to consider the case of huge pages and the\nsame folio if retrieved for many pages.\n\nSo the original offset to the page must be passed down\nand used when working with the pages in bulk r/w and\npage encryption.\n\nThis prepares the osc brw for handing such folios.\n\n{duplicate not for landing}\n\nTest-Parameters: forbuildonly\nHPE-bug-id: LUS-12384\nSigned-off-by: Shaun Tancheff <shaun.tancheff@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I666e4d6dd963d85a5791d938f66115c879f4bb69\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
